OL,5,FSomewhat prophetically, her first ever
OL,6,Fradio report involved covering the
OL,7,Fhottest day of the year and frying an
OL,8,Fegg on the pavement ` two of her
OL,9,Ffavourite interests, weather and
OL,10,Fcooking!JWhen she's not scratting
OL,11,Faround in the garden or the kitchen,
OL,12,Fthis one-woman wildlife feeding
OL,13,Fstation enjoys dinner and a musical,
OL,14,Flanguages and observational comedy,
OL,15,Freformer pilates - and when there's
OL,16,Ftime - sleeping.
